  "measurement": "Cannot be measured with use counters because the URL parser is used in many places in Chrome, and not all of them have access to an ExecutionContext or similar.\n\nUMA could be used and give a proportion of URL parses affected metric, but given how many URLs are parsed and how rare even valid IDNA URLs seem to be, the number is probably vanishingly small and not informative of risk.",
